<small>Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Atari_Punk_Console&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Atari_Punk_Console&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve the article</a> with a <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Writing_better_articles#Lead_section" title="Wikipedia:Writing better articles">good introductory style</a>. <i>(April 2007)</i></small></td>
